            "is_accepted": true,
            "last_activity_date": 1344565342,
            "creation_date": 1344565342,
            "body": "<p>Thanks for all the efforts you have made . Finally , I think I have found the answer.<\/p>\n\n<p>Instead of dealing with the string in java program, I process the string using sql functions directly.<\/p>\n\n<p>Following is what I do.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>SELECT * substring(path,len(path)-charindex('\\',reverse(path))+2,charindex('\\',reverse(path)))\n FROM News\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>This really does a good job !!<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 11894615,
            "question_id": 11876568
        }
